    <p>Except as may be set forth in this Privacy Policy, Online Data related to OBA is retained by Ziff Davis for not more than 180 days after which it shall expire. However, the 180 day period may commence again if the same user subsequently visits or interacts with an ad, email, the Services or a Channel.</p>
